/* fonts */
export const FontFamily = {
  latoRegular: "Lato_regular",
  robotoRegular: "Roboto_regular",
  robotoSemibold: "Roboto_semibold",
  interSemibold: "Inter_semibold",
  robotoLight: "Roboto_light",
  robotoExtrabold: "Roboto_extrabold",
  robotoMedium: "Roboto_medium",
  interMedium: "Inter_medium",
  robotoBold: "Roboto_bold",
  poppinsRegular: "Poppins_regular",
  poppinsBold: "Poppins_bold",
  poppinsBlack: "Poppins_black",
  poppinsSemibold: "Poppins_semibold",
};
/* font sizes */
export const FontSize = {
  size_sm: 14,
  size_3xl: 22,
  size_xl: 20,
  size_lg: 18,
  size_mini: 15,
  size_smi: 13,
  size_base: 16,
  size_xs: 12,
  size_mid: 17,
  size_6xl: 25,
  size_lgi: 19,
  size_xs_3: 11,
};
/* Colors */
export const Color = {
  gray_100: "#272a35",
  gray_200: "#0e1936",
  gray_400: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6)",
  gray_300: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)",
  gray_500: "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25)",
  gray_600: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3)",
  white: "#fff",
  skyblue_100: "#4ec6e0",
  skyblue_200: "rgba(78, 198, 224, 0.44)",
  skyblue_300: "rgba(78, 198, 224, 0)",
  darkgray_100: "#b4b4b4",
  darkgray_200: "#9e9ca5",
  gainsboro_100: "#dadae3",
  gainsboro_200: "#d9d9d9",
  deepskyblue: "rgba(3, 169, 241, 0.6)",
  darkNeutral: "#414247",
  darkslategray_100: "#373e4e",
  darkslategray_200: "rgba(72, 72, 72, 0.3)",
  mediumseagreen: "#00ac83",
  red_100: "#ff0a01",
  red_200: "#ff0000",
  silver: "#b9b9b9",
  cornflowerblue: "#4c9eeb",
  slategray: "#5d6a8b",
  peachpuff: "#ffdfba",
  accentRoyalBlue200: "#d6e4ff",
};
/* Paddings */
export const Padding = {
  p_2xl: 21,
  p_6xs: 7,
  p_sm: 14,
  p_base: 16,
};
/* Margins */
export const Margin = {
  m_11xs: 2,
  m_9xs: 4,
  m_base: 16,
};
/* border radiuses */
export const Border = {
  br_10xs_5: 3,
  br_11xl: 30,
  br_10xl: 29,
  br_81xl: 100,
  br_xl: 20,
  br_3xs: 10,
  br_11xs: 2,
  br_31xl: 50,
  br_21xl: 40,
  br_4xs: 9,
  br_xs: 12,
  br_base: 16,
};
